items.name: Solving-BSE-Numerically
items.description: This repository contains the implementation of numerical methods for solving the Black-Scholes Equation and the Time-Dependent Schrödinger Equation. It features C++ code using the Crank-Nicolson method, along with Python scripts for visualizing the results. A detailed report analyzing the findings and methodologies is also included.
